PLACEHOLDER — replace this file with a real 1200×630 PNG before launch.

Recommended design:
  - Background: #1a1a2e (navy) or a gradient from #1a1a2e to #2d2d4e
  - Logo: "♥ HarmoHelp" in white, large, bold (top-left or centered)
  - Tagline: "Hormonal Wellness Platform" in #D4B83A (gold) below the logo
  - Optional: a subtle wellness wave graphic or a screenshot of the dashboard
  - Bottom strip: "harmohelp.com" in small cream text

Tools to generate this image:
  - Figma / Canva (free)
  - https://og-playground.vercel.app
  - satori (npm) for code-generated OG images

File requirements:
  - Exactly 1200 × 630 pixels
  - PNG or JPG, under 8 MB (under 1 MB recommended for performance)
  - Place the final file at: public/og-image.png
  - Update the og:image meta in index.html if the filename changes
